xxl.binarySearchTrees
Class BinarySearchTree.LevelOrderIterator

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--xxl.binarySearchTrees.BinarySearchTree.LevelOrderIterator
Enclosing class:
BinarySearchTree
public class BinarySearchTree.LevelOrderIterator
extends Object
implements Iterator

Inner class implementing level order traversal through the tree. During a level order traversal, nodes have to be stored in memory. This is done in a ListQueue internally. The queue can contain |leaf nodes| Nodes at maximum. Currently, the remove operation is not supported (throws an UnsupportedOperationExcetion).
